OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FThe sisters and brother of a young
OL,7,Ffather-to-be who drowned shortly after
OL,8,Fhis eighteenth birthday have spoken
OL,9,Fout publicly for the first time in the
OL,10,Fhope of preventing further tragedies.
OL,12,FBenjamin Glen was walking along the
OL,13,FRiver Nith in Dumfries on the 30th
OL,14,FApril when his family believe he went
OL,15,Finto the water to retrieve something
OL,16,Fand got into difficulty.
OL,18,FHis siblings described Ben as a
OL,19,F"cheeky young man" who would "do
OL,20,Fanything for anyone."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
