PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FAged 13, 15 and 21, they say they can
OL,7,Fno longer give their brother a hug,
OL,8,Fwatch him play computer games, or see
OL,9,Fhim walk through the door asking for
OL,10,Fmac and cheese.
OL,12,FHis eldest sister, Abigail, 21,
OL,13,Frecalls waiting for a bus when she
OL,14,Freceived a phone call.
OL,16,FAbigail said: "I answered it, and they
OL,17,Fsaid your brother is in the River
OL,18,FNith, he's drowned. My heart dropped,
OL,19,Feverything was a blur to me, I was
OL,20,Fjust running to where he was.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,F"I heard the sirens and I didn't think
OL,7,Fthat was for Ben. My heart just
OL,8,Fdropped."
OL,10,FThe family say they are grateful to
OL,11,Fthe emergency services, who later
OL,12,Frecovered Ben's body.
OL,14,FAbigail told ITV Border that Ben "went
OL,15,Funder in seconds", explaining that
OL,16,Fpeople don't understand the dangers of
OL,17,Fopen water.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FShe continued: "I think the water
OL,7,Fwould've shocked him, and this is what
OL,8,Fpeople don't realise. Whether it's 20
OL,9,Fdegrees or 25 degrees outside, that
OL,10,Fwater is still cold and people don't
OL,11,Frealise that.
OL,13,F"He went under in seconds because of
OL,14,Fthe undercurrent, and people don't
OL,15,Frealise that either.
OL,17,F"When we were there the water looked
OL,18,Fshallow, it did look shallow, I
OL,19,Fthought 'I could put my toes in that',
OL,20,Fbut you don't realise how deep and how
OL,21,Ffast the tide comes in."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FBen's younger sister, Holly-Rose, 15,
OL,7,Fsaid "Just be careful when you go in
OL,8,Fwater, because no matter what that
OL,9,Fwater can kill you, you can get shock
OL,10,Ffrom it, how deep it is, just don't go
OL,11,Fin."
OL,13,FThirteen-year-old Oliver said: "I told
OL,14,Fall my friends to respect the water,
OL,15,Fbe safe when you're in it, respect it
OL,16,Fat all times."
OL,18,FBen's siblings believe more awareness
OL,19,Fis needed in schools, extra signage
OL,20,Fnear rivers, and instructions on how
OL,21,Fto use life rings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
