FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FAt least 17 people died after getting
OL,7,Finto trouble in open water during the
OL,8,Frecent heatwave in May. Ben's siblings
OL,9,Fsay it's been hard to see.
OL,11,FHolly-Rose said: "I know how those
OL,12,Ffamilies feel, it's triggering, it's
OL,13,Fhard, I feel bad for the families.
OL,15,F"I've seen people on TikTok live
OL,16,Fjumping in rivers, and it's just awful.
OL,18,F"I just want the awareness to go out,
OL,19,Fstay out of water."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780596668
OL,3,C'It's impacted me a lot': Calls for
OL,4,Cmore water safety awareness
OL,6,FAbigail added: "Over the past week
OL,7,Fit's been hot and seeing videos of
OL,8,Fpeople jumping in rivers and I'm like,
OL,9,FI've just lost my brother because of
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,FThe reality of the dangers of open
OL,13,Fwater is something these three young
OL,14,Fpeople now have to live with every day.
OL,16,FHolly-Rose said: "It's impacted me a
OL,17,Flot, I can't go near water, I hate
OL,18,Fgoing near the River Nith, even the
OL,19,Fshower scares me."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
